text: Bichelsee-Balterswil is a municipality of the district of Münchwilen in the canton of Thurgau in Switzerland. It was made from the union on January 1, 1996 of Bichelsee and Balterswil. The lake Bichelsee is in the municipality. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Municipalities in Münchwilen
title: Bichelsee-Balterswil
